<H3> <TI>   Opposition Groups, Parties Meet </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Opposition Groups, Parties Meet </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0695C Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY in Russian 26 Apr 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> 944F0695C </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
