<H3> <TI>   Opposition Party Strives for Solidarity </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Opposition Party Strives for Solidarity </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0698B Moscow LITERATURNAYA ROSSIYA in Russian 22 Apr 94 
p 11 </F>

<F P=103> 944F0698B </F>
