<H3> <TI>   Local Investment, Inflation Rates Compared </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Local Investment, Inflation Rates Compared </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0707A Novosibirsk SOVETSKAYA SIBIR in Russian 13 May 94 
p 1 </F>

<F P=103> 944F0707A </F>
<F P=104>  Novosibirsk SOVETSKAYA SIBIR </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


