<H3> <TI>   Environment for Business Examined </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Environment for Business Examined </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0700A Novosibirsk SOVETSKAYA SIBIR in Russian 12 May 94 
p 2 </F>

