<H3> <TI>   Regional Press Agencies Plan Cooperation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Regional Press Agencies Plan Cooperation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1248B Almaty KAZAKHSTANSKAYA PRAVDA in Russian 17 May 94 
p 1 </F>

<F P=103> 944K1248B </F>
<F P=104>  Almaty KAZAKHSTANSKAYA PRAVDA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


