<F P=101> ECONOMIC AND SOCIAL AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Press Committee Head Mironov Profiled </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Press Committee Head Mironov Profiled </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0684B Moscow OBSHCHAYA GAZETA in Russian No 18, 6 May 94 
p 8 </F>

<F P=103> 944F0684B </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow OBSHCHAYA GAZETA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


