<H3> <TI>   Nuclear Repair Industry Union Makes Third Government Appeal </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Nuclear Repair Industry Union Makes Third Government Appeal </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944E0811B Moscow RABOCHAYA TRIBUNA in Russian 13 May 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 944E0811B </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow RABOCHAYA TRIBUNA </F>
