<H3> <TI>   Government Session Reviews Spring Call Up </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Government Session Reviews Spring Call Up </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1247A Yerevan RESPUBLIKA ARMENIYA in Russian 17 May 94 p 
1 </F>

<F P=103> 944K1247A </F>
