<H3> <TI>   Prime Minister Reviews Domestic, Foreign Policy </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Prime Minister Reviews Domestic, Foreign Policy </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1205A Riga NEATKARIGA CINA in Latvian 20 Apr 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 944K1205A </F>
<F P=104>  Riga NEATKARIGA CINA </F>
